text: De Moortel or Van De Moortel is a surname. It is the surname of: *Arie Van de Moortel (1918–1976), Belgian musician and composer *Françoise Van De Moortel (1941–2005), Belgian journalist *Ineke De Moortel, Belgian applied mathematician *Joris van de Moortel, Belgian artist in BiennaleOnline *Mathilde Van de Moortel, winner of the 2016 César Award for Best Editing
title: De Moortel
